lead_paragraph: ROSENBERG--Andrea, 71, of East Brunswick, NJ passed away November 29, 2014. Predeceased by husband William in 2013, survived by her three children, eight grandchildren and her brother. Service will be held Monday, December 1, 2014 at AEMT, New Brunswick, NJ at 10 am. 1/3
